BackEnd
Class BackEndJar

java.lang.Object
  BackEnd.BackEndJar

public class BackEndJar
extends java.lang.Object

This class parses a string containing git log commit info sent by a Jenkins script and adds each newly parsed commit as it's own .txt file in HDFS under the appropriate year, month, day, and hour folders (each a sub-folder of the one before it).
